Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.82,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}be they criminals or actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The weird code that Doc came up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's tougher than the Detective Boys expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.70,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who will solve it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.51,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
