Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.16,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}One hot summer day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.84,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}we were out to collect bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.71,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Doc gave us a code quiz,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:06.39,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"marumushi ni tento", which would lead us to where a treasure was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But I couldn't solve the code either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.69,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Meanwhile, Ran and Sonoko called me from the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:18.46,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}saying there was a murder at the hotel where they were staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:24.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sonoko remembered seeing some strange writing{14:05}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the window of the room where the murder took place...{14:09}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange writing?{14:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like some kind of code...{14:18}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who found the body?{17:14}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:38.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of Miyama-{\i1}san{\i0}'s friends!{17:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were going out to dinner together.{17:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:48.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Miyama-{\i1}san{\i0} didn't show up on time, they went to his room and found the door unlocked.{17:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:53.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They went inside and found Miyama-{\i1}san{\i0} lying on the ground under a broken window.{17:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what they told the police.{17:47}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.07,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After that, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:04.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Then maybe the "tento" part of the code refers to the Tentō Festival!{21:43}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:08.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, I don't understand the "marumushi" in front of it.{21:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the direction of the Marumushi Hot Spring!{22:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Marumushi ni tentō" - "Light up the Marumushi"...{22:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?{arere}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's some mysterious gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real. Take a closer look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're carrying washbowls, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The village probably bought this run-down inn on the cheap and turned it into a public bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bath... sentō...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe tento is really sentō! You know, a public bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, that "te" doesn't look like a "se".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:12.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not tentō, as in "light", either. It's clearly spelled tento.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:22.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Genta. You can't just collapse and give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Doc said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:31.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said we might be able to solve the code if we lay down and thought about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:40.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we're stuck, we should splash water on our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've got a public bath here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take her advice and wash off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me, you won't find anything in that inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if a {\i1}certain someone{\i0} also gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Give up, my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A text...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:24.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey. I thought Sonoko had her bag stolen with her cell phone inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"I found this bag abandoned on a street,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but there was nothing to identify the owner by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:36.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I checked the cell phone I found inside the bag
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and decided to send a message to the most recent person on the list of calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:46.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I would like to send the bag to you, so please give me your name and address."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:50.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh. I guess the purse snatcher threw Sonoko's bag away after stealing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why isn't this person asking me for the address of the owner of the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:03.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And why text me? Wouldn't it be easier to just call someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You give up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:16.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Or they could hand the bag over to the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hello, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received a text from someone who claims to have found Sonoko's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.69,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:30.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They may contact you too. Wait for the call...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:30.95,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:32.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My phone's almost dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the police station now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll call you back as soon as we get to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you told them the message might be "tel shite", "please call"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:50.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and Miyama-{\i1}san{\i0}'s three friends said that could be a possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't identify the murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're going back to the hotel for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful. That purse snatcher could still be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.58,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I asked Kano-{\i1}san{\i0} to drive me and your wife to the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:19.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran told you, didn't she? Miyama's hot college friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are his other two friends there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It'll be just us and Kano-{\i1}san{\i0}, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:33.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are taking a long time to question Yanuma-{\i1}san{\i0}, the late Miyama-{\i1}san{\i0}'s girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano-{\i1}san{\i0}'s been waiting for her to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bito-{\i1}san{\i0} walked back to the hotel on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:45.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yanuma-{\i1}san{\i0} is crying and the police still have questions for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:50.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so Kano-{\i1}san{\i0}'s going to drive us to the hotel and then come back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.36,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.44,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, I'd better hang up! My phone's almost dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:56.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish I'd gone to the beach with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of the beach, I found a jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find a jellyfish in the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish when it's upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.54,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish when it's upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see... So that's what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Lie down and splash water on your face, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}a code like this gave me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But sometimes, simple codes are the hardest to decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been long enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just tell us the secret code?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "marumushi ni tento" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:28.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Until you all give up, my lips are sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I give up! Whisper it to me! Where's the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why did I suddenly think of Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come on, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't solved it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make any sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a sore loser, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys give up too easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like even Shin'ichi is stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about this carefully from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the code is written in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand "marumushi" and "tento" being written in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, doesn't it seem strange that a word like "ni" would be written that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:22.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Secondly, if you look closely, each character is strangely crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc's just got bad handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And thirdly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we've got the clues Doc and Haibara gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did they ever give us clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lie down and think about it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and "if you don't get it, splash some water on your face."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't things they normally say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they want us to lie down and look at the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything different...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:24.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, for a sec I thought I had it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you or didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:31.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I was sure the message would say something sideways!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the smirk on his smug little face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's solved it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:49.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even sideways, it doesn't look like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's think about the other clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:59.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about washing your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to wash up in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:07.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think we're supposed to go to that in the villagers use as a public bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara and the Doc already told us there's nothing at the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where are we supposed to wash up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:17.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she didn't literally mean "wash your face".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think. What do you do when you wash your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the tap...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash up in the running water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe my face with a towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:45.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}, we're talking about when you wash your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After I wash my face, I eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I look in the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't see anything in the mirror but yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This just gets more baffling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think you're on to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,see how that hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when it's upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of these letters look like fish upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't look like words either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:17.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have to do both!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the message sideways and reflect it in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we turn it sideways, flip it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold it up to the moonlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,(ムラマツリノトリイ MU RA MA TSU RI NO TO RI I)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"muramatsuri no tori'i" - "the shrine of the village festival"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"muramatsuri no tori'i" ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's that shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Doc? Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:06.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:21.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you taught the kids they can figure things out on their own if they put their minds to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I'm a heck of a guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to go look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to find out what the treasure is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:42.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The code points to that brightly-lit tori'i gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you smeared some tree sap onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's swarming with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhinoceros beetles and stag beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you came up with this secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A message that can be read from different directions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Ai-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to use animals for the code first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:28.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I taped animal names to the window to get ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:32.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was doing that, Ai-{\i1}kun{\i0} was watching from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.87,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Isn't 'oxygen' too advanced for the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:42.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... "kirin" (キリン) or "giraffe" looked like "sanso" (サンソ) from the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you thought of the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought of Ran a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran's in serious danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're on the way back to the hotel in Kano-{\i1}san{\i0}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the car right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.55,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've figured out the real meaning of "teiu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:45.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There was a small splotch in front of the "t"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The message was written sideways,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but stand it up and flip it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it spells the murderer's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The battery's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it? What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:07.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about standing up and flipping over the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like your husband's jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:19.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ran and Sonoko are involved in a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:25.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko happened to see the letters of a message written by a man who was bludgeoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was written horizontally in lowercase letters that spelled "teiu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More precisely, there was a little mark in front of the "t",
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:38.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the "i" was an "l" and the "u" looked like a hiragana "shi" (し).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like "muramatsuri no tori'i".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The message is written sideways and backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"marumushi ni tento" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn "sanso" on its side and read it backwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kirin".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's "teiu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,かのう - the characters for "Kano".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the victim leave such a difficult code as a dying message?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no code!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed on the floor and wrote the name on the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sonoko saw it from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to tell Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but Ran's phone went dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran and Sonoko are in Kano's car right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the road to the hotel, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Where's the hotel they're staying at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:19:00.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew that, I would've called the cops already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All Ran told me was that she was going to the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I should've realized it sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:12.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I got that weird text message from Sonoko's stolen phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to delete the picture with the dying message from my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he asked for my name and address...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0} guy you were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a teen detective, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool! Dating a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! He's not my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a cute couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:47.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I sent him a photo of Ran in her swimsuit this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A pity Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0} isn't here with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've loved to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that sleuth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:03.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{SUBTITLE MISSING}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the murderer is waiting for me to contact him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he must have Sonoko's phone on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Listen to that ringtone, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:21.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That ringtone's the same as your phone, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, rather, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is{\i0} my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I grabbed it off you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get rid of the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get deeper into the woods, I've got some questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about the whereabouts of that Shin'ichi brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't picked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:07.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Someone's picked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "hello" me! Where the hell were you when Ran needed you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:47.59,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! Are you listening to me?!{possibly missing the end of the line}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, um, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:51.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've been hurt when the car crashed into that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:53.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The car?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it was, we had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:03.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran's side kick went straight into the driver's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:05.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.72,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After that, Sonoko called the police, and the murderer was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:16.96,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The victim had been blackmailing Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:20.71,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}threatening to reveal the fact that he'd cheated his way into college.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:27.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was the same old story of one crime snowballing into another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:30.59,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:31.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I thought I saved it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:39.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, we deleted that swimsuit photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:41.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Kids can't look at that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:48.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We had Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0} erase it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:54.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}DAMN!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:02.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Magure's such a great show, isn't it?{DCTP 2:26}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really outdid yourselves with the trick that time.{DCTP 3:07}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is one of the drama's three scriptwriters, isn't he?{DCTP 4:20}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.87,0:24:16.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Such an aggressive look in his eyes...{DCTP 13:21}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's definitely the culprit.{DCTP 13:24}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:23.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yet he has so much confidence in his trick.{DCTP 13:28}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:30.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:35.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Two cups
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:36.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The next episode's title...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:39.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If it's half-finished, then maybe it's a boxed eel lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:40.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
